{{Documentation subpage}}
{{nosubst}}
{{Uses TemplateStyles}}
{{Style|lists}}
The '''{{tlx|Style}}''' template is used on pages belonging to the [[Wikipedia:Manual of Style|Manual of Style]].

Place this sidebar template at the top of pages relevant to the Manual of Style.

== Collapsible lists ==
{{Collapsible lists option
| listnames = {{ublist |{{hlist|content|formatting|images|layout|lists|legal}} |{{hlist|by topic area (arts|regional|religion|science|sports)}} |related}}
|example = lists
}}

== See also ==
* {{lts|MoS-guideline}} for MoS subpages.
* {{lts|Subcat guideline}} for other guidelines not necessarily part of the Wikipedia MoS.
* {{tl|Manual of Style}}, the Navbox version of this template intended for use at the bottom of a page.
* [[Wikipedia:Template messages/Cleanup#Style of writing|Wikipedia:Template messages/Cleanup §&nbsp;Style of writing]]

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other|
| <!-- CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE, PLEASE: -->
[[Category:Wikipedia Manual of Style templates]]
[[Category:Wikipedia guideline templates]]
}}</includeonly>

